Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.89,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きそうな　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.06,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,青リンゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.98,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱えてる胸の奥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.98,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,転がって　強がって　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.94,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,窮屈な空睨む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:26.78,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,運命に 従順に　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:33.99,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,熟すのを 待つもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.52,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,千の風（あがいて）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:43.58,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,吹け吹け（叫んで）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:47.56,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,わたしは（それでも）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:51.58,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,しゃぼん玉（信じてる）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.57,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,予期せぬ（上昇して）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:59.63,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,嵐に（下降して）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.57,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あらがう（それでも）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:07.50,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,しゃぼん玉（生きてく）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.45,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,弾ける瞬間　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:13.91,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,虹、放て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.89,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,快哭出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.06,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,青苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.98,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紧抱在胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.98,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,摔倒 逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.94,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着狭小的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:26.78,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,谁愿意顺从地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:33.99,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,等待命运成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.52,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,千之风（不断挣扎）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:43.58,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吹吧吹吧（嘶喊着）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:47.56,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是（即便如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:51.58,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱之泡沫（依然坚信）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.57,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,无法预测（上浮）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:59.63,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,向风暴（下沉）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.57,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,做抗争（即便如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:07.50,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱之泡沫（依旧独活）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.45,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,破裂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:13.91,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,..虹光四射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:32.07,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：背景乐为德沃夏克e小调第九交响曲《自新大陆》（又名《自新世界》《归途》）节选
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ByeBye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想赶快回去..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么..这样算平手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾 明明我们差一点就要赢了说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快点投降啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 是我们这边占优耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚才不是我们占优势吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们连旗子都没夺走 我们怎么可能投降呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉 你为什么要帮敌人说话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是规则啦规则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日落的时候比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳不是还没下山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你站在高处才看得见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理亚 该赶紧回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一听到《归途》就必须赶紧回家了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你们投降的话就马上能回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“嗯”你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁判根本没有好好在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁判快点宣布比赛握手言和啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别太过分了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 今天算是平手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 瞬！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啦 明明还没结束的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回家啦 因为猫怪会跑出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季 我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里 看得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓑白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 那个一点都不稀奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年之后 茨城 神栖六十六町
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫩叶的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这个破庙的和尚 名叫无瞋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是渡边早季
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问..这里 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座寺庙名为清净寺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问..这里在八丁标的外面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你自出生以来第一次跨出八丁标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么从现在开始我要焚烧成长之护摩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:00.23,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：护摩，梵语homa，为火祭，焚烧之意，即投供物于火中之火祭祀法。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们燃尽最后一项烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注视火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请试着操控火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 你做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请试着让火焰晃动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从左向右摇摇曳曳..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祝灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于也发生在你身上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是..？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就意味着早季也变成大人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天也从和贵园中毕业了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以进入完人学校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不用担心什么了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止！请住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后剩下来的那项烦恼即是你的这股咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请抛弃烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须暂且让所有烦恼在清净之炎中燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们把上天赐予你的能力还给神佛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从现在起要将你的咒力封印进这个人形之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请操纵人形让它站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己所有的感情都注入那个人形之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡边早季！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的咒力已经被封印在此处！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃尽所有的烦恼 让余尘回归无边的荒土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的咒力消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注视火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经无法操纵火焰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..已经深深皈依于神佛 自愿放弃了自己的咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 我将在此传授你正确的真言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招聘新的精灵 再一次将咒力赋予于你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真言..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是从今天起要成为你们新同学的渡边早季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在我旁边就好了呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女孩子呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守是友爱园毕业的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是呀 我都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大器晚成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是早来就一定有好的祝灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可在和贵园组中却是倒数第一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说都悠闲过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉跟我也差不了多少嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？倒数第一？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后还有好几人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污秽 归来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完人学校中不仅有学科
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有能力实技呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗？在波纹干涉方面我的成绩是班级中顶尖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过在击力交换方面却完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:09:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师说过 现阶段最重要的是成像能力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..是妙法农场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和那里很像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里像了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在和贵园的时候不是去参观过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是不是袋牛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 长着袋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里很像这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得气氛很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二节课是关于恶鬼和业魔的课哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶~还要上那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太喜欢那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与在和贵园学的不一样 是完全版哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天请秋月同学..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是发生于距现在大约五百年前的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一位少年在大山深处采收药草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在仔细寻找的过程中..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不知不觉来到了八丁标的注连绳之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不经意地往前一看..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现绳子外面还长着很多没采收的药草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去大人就一再叮嘱他不能走到八丁标的外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在迫不得已的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则必须在大人的陪同下走出绳外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看到对面有一个恶鬼朝他走来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶鬼想要让他带着自己回到村落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就这样把恶鬼带回村落的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村落就会遭遇灭顶之灾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该如何是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我的性命并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要让恶鬼靠近村落”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此以后 直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶鬼就再也没有出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 那么各位请翻回第一页 再一次把内容..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细节部分也要仔细地想象出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说不定能看见作者心中的投影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 瞬好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 守
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换真理亚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 嗯 干得不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是丽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了哦 丽子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:21.28,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.72,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:23.53,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮有一套的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从头再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会输哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度不能再快一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没有差你多少嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输给你的 放心好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 同班之间竞争有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看五班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的情况好得不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们的王牌依旧是状态神勇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 也有扯后腿的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有丽子在 我们班就不可能优胜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？！丽子是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过有点状态不好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻不傻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 为什么没邀请丽子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怕她有顾虑啦 顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟把比赛搞砸成那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一起回家的话 她自己反而受不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她也太容易道歉了啦 我听了都烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一班的能力很高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有瞬在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对啊 瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我..没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为丽子一直搞失败 我们才得不到优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我听说也有人没能从和贵园毕业 读到一半就消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季 那只是传言啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不在意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是谣言 不过我曾经听人讲过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在打开那扇门的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能从门外稍微窥探到中庭的样子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有非常多的坟墓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是恐怖故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是谁的坟墓呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是有很多很多的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要特地在学校的中庭里造坟墓啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我哪知道那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么坟墓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬你看见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是有一次收不齐作业的答案纸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理科的自由观察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师让我收齐所有人的答案再送去给他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就进入了管理栋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然从那里能看见中庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是排列在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用砖瓦砌起来的 类似库房的建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之不是坟墓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相大白 果然只是觉的恐怖故事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的是听人这么说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和贵园的恐怖故事还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 好怕好怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些什么故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守啊 我不是说不想听了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在和贵园啊 有人看见过另一个可怕的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常巨大的猫的身影..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是猫怪？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说猫怪经常在学校出没哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问吗 因为它专挑小孩子下手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在秋天的傍晚经常会出没哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也会在家的附近来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过来的时候大都是夜半时分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 早早地从和贵园毕业并没有什么了不起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和咒力的强弱以及质量一点关系都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你爸其实都不算快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不是最后一名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样没错啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的没法毕业的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法毕业的话 猫怪就会来迎接你的那个传说是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个小笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫怪这种东西根本不存在于这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明马上就要成为大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还在说这种话会被别人笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..你在说什么呀 只是错觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季？早季？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个传说在和贵园的时候就很有名了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才害怕起来是要怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！觉你闭嘴啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛..你认真生什么气啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 得快点回家了呢 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算遇上猫怪我也不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 看到的话还不被它吞下肚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说一开始不会攻击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁说的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁来着..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ByeBye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季 完人学校怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算有趣..吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“吧？”是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不干脆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为才刚刚入学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还不太明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是大致还行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真担心呢 这样下去 但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等等吧 你这么着急的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而会给她带去坏影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都上了些什么课呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用纸牌做金字塔..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有沙画之类的..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 和爸爸妈妈读的时候没什么差别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸可喜欢恶作剧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用假巢蛇的蛋乱砸学校的铜像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果被那时还是校长的无瞋上人狠狠教训了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你提那么早的事情做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样下去的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 教育委员会差不多该有所动作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用图书馆的权限很难对委员会产生影响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是裁决权者 只要有那个意思就一定能做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委员会是独立的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的职权根本无从查起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说如果我以早季父亲的立场提出那种意见..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不要再失去孩子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..早季说她看到不净猫了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是她看错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的的话怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季？早季？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝灵也顺利到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清净寺也去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完人学校的学习也开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈我松了一大口气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松了一口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不要再失去孩子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松了一口气是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..松了一口气是理所当然的反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈的祝灵也蛮晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的父母也都很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 早季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人类能使用咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那只是非常渺小的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以必须要多加珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此要好好地..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在几天之后 天野丽子的身影..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从学校消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年对自己的聪慧过于骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对所有的一切都不屑一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲慢会种下业的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独会成为业的温床
